<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF108-627-110  </DOCNO><DOCID>08 627 110.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>Newsbytes  May 10 1990* Full Text COPYRIGHT Newsbytes Inc. 1990.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Suzy up and running. (on line information service)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Buckler, Grant.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   Stratford Software Corp. (marketing).andO;Topic:     Information servicesSuzy (Information retrieval system)On-LineInformation Storage and Retrieval.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>SUZY UP AND RUNNING VANCOUVER, BRITISH COLUMBIA, CANADA, 1990 MAY 7 (NB) --After several delays, the new Suzy online information service is inoperation.andM;Stratford Software began shipping the software for its new service in lateApril, spokesman Terry McDonald told Newsbytes.andP;  The software is beingdistributed in Canada through Ingram Micro D and Softsel.andP;  It is alsoavailable through offices of Marathon Brokerage, a nationwide realtor.andP;  Thesoftware costs C$29.95, McDonald said, and connect-time charges are C$12 perhour for most services, with discounts in off-peak hours and surcharges forsome services.andM;Suzy offers a variety of information services, such as stock market data,airline and hotel information, national real estate listings and newsservices, in addition to electronic mail and conferencing facilities.andO;Public-domain software is also available for downloading.andM;McDonald said Stratford will continue to enhance Suzy with further services.andO;The company will also be exploring additional distribution channels, he said.andM;(Grant Buckler/19900508/Press Contact: Terry McDonald, Stratford Software,604-439-1311)</TEXT></DOC>